INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('hina115',389,'2016-09-16',5,'Jeff and Rick are very knowledgeable and down to earth hosts. Their very spacious upper west side apartment is only 10-15 mins to Times Square on the subway number 1 train. The AirBnB private suite has its own renovated shower and toilet and good walk in closet space and ample drawers to put your clothes in. You also have Netflix to keep you entertained unless you dont mind a chin wag with them in the kitchen. They are a 5 minute stroll to our favourite 24 hour diner and great Chinese dine in or takeaway. There is also a great New York sucks pizza place up near 91st Street which I had to try .... delicious! It also has a Kosher marketplace near by as well. One fond memory is Jeff and Rick took us to Carmines up the road a must do as the shared chicken wings were amazing. Last but least we had so much fun with their small dog Buster which you can have as much or as little to do with him as you please. All in all a fantastic place with great memories and hosts. Thoroughly recommend a visit to Jeffs pad.',8);
