INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pellentesque33136',3894,'2019-06-26',5,'This place was perfect. Close to the subway, Hells Kitchen, Time Square. I had a great time. Would highly recommend it and would definitely book again',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('dui8069',3984,'2021-09-04',5,'This was a great location, only 6 minute walk from Port Authority/Subway, with some nice dining options within a block or two. The apartment was small but very clean with super soft sheets and a very comfortable bed. The bathroom in the hall (outside of the apartment) wasn t ideal but it worked out. My only complaint was the construction going on at daylight on Saturday right next door. If you are an early riser, not a problem but if you like sleeping in, it s hard to do when the jack hammers get going. There were no workers on Sunday so it was quiet. Overall, I would stay again.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut35181',4715,'2020-05-17',4,'Luiz was a great host! The only thing that kept me from giving the fifth star was the bathroom being in the hallway and the shower being a little bit small. All in all it was a great experience!',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sapien72146',3970,'2017-10-14',5,'Note: This review is for the room with the bunk-style bed.I was pleasantly surprised by how wonderful my stay here at Luiz s place was. The room is a standard small room for NY but it felt so much bigger because the bed was not in the way. Since it is raised above, there was more space to maneuver and relax! I loved this feature the most because I could set up my laptop station at the sofa area under the bed which had a height clearance of probably 6  (maybe less)? I m 5 3 so I was able to walk under the bunk area just fine.Getting to the bed area was fine for me, but you will have to be very careful in watching where you step. There s not much to hold on to except for the railing of the bunk ladder and the side of the bed. Once there though, it is fantastic. The mattress was soft yet firm enough to offer plenty of back support. The sheets were soft and clean. There s a lamp next to the mattress for added light in the dark. Then the best part is the tv that is stationed right in front of you with so many channels to choose from a Roku system that is connected to the apartment s Netflix account (and a few others too).Your sleep will be sound here! Of all the nights I stayed here in this room, I barely heard any outside noise! Usually the nightlife of NY is loud, especially in the bustling streets of Times Square! So I was rather surprised how quiet it was here despite the fantastic location. I think it was that the room s window was turned away from the streets, and the room is on the second floor of the building.For those who make bathroom visits in the middle of the night, it may be a bit inconvenient as the toilet is actually outside the apartment in the hallway behind a locked door. So you ll have to climb down the bunkbed, remember to grab the keys, put shoes on, go out of the apartment and down the hall, and unlock the door to the toilet room. This didn t bother me much though, considering how lovely the rest of the stay is.Right outside the apartment are so many convenient shops and lots of restaurants to choose from. I defaulted to the korean fried chicken joint during nights when I was too lazy to go on food adventures after a long day out. A couple blocks from Port Authority, this place was so easy to find when coming in from the airport. The reason of my stay here was for a convention at Javits so this place was the perfect location as it was a mere few blocks away from the convention center as well.I definitely recommend staying here if you can. The stay was great and Luiz is a very kind, gracious host.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('cursus11108',3464,'2018-07-25',5,'Luiz place is exactly as described in the photos, it might be weird or uncomfortable for some the fact that the toilet is outside of the apartment and the bathroom is really small but it s totally understandable for NYC-like spaces. The place was clean and bed was very comfortable, great location. Good deal for travelers looking for a place to crash after exploring NYC.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit9598',4558,'2019-09-30',4,'Luiz was the best and allowed me to do an early check in. The apartment is in a great location close to everything.. the tiolet is out in the hall but it s not bad at all. I loved my room and experience at this location.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et4430',466,'2016-10-31',5,'This is a nice place to sleep. The bed is really comfy, though it is loft style. Be aware that the bathroom is down the hall and you need a key (which is provided). The shower is in the apartment but is very tight and has a tiny sink. The best part about this apartment is the location. Very close to everything and the subway is just a few blocks away.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('viverra37167',1402,'2018-04-28',5,'Had a great time. It was as described and clean.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl1470',2857,'2021-05-27',5,'I had a great stay with Luiz.  In the heart of Hell s Kitchen so it is great for walking to many of the key sites.  Great A/C and secure building.  The area is noisy but it is also the heart of NYC so it is to be expected.  Thanks Luiz',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('convallis3283',2794,'2019-06-04',5,'A great location and price! Luiz was accommodating and the place was nice. It is an old building so the bathroom and shower are small spaces.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eu25190',1942,'2019-02-01',4,'Perfect location, excellent host, great experience!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit22151',2158,'2019-10-09',5,'Communication from Luiz was quick and clear. The apartment, while small, was clean and well-equipped.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae1580',305,'2019-10-27',5,'Great space in a great area. Close to so many places you want to visit! The toilet for this apartment is in the hall and is small. I had no difficulties and never saw anyone in the hallway. The bed was super comfy. It is a loft bed so make sure you can get up a ladder.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sem33132',2959,'2020-12-15',4,'The place is a much more affordable option than a hotel. The area is much more interesting than staying in midtown. It was a real comfortable & clean place to stay.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et4430',663,'2017-12-17',5,'Absolutely loved the location and my room. The bed was super comfortable and it felt like I was at home. I felt like a real New Yorker which made the trip that much better. I would definitely stay with Luiz again!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut1923',3129,'2018-02-05',5,'Such a great little apartment in the middle of everything! The place was small, but an excellent home base to get out and explore. The host was also very friendly and responsive.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ligula35188',4164,'2020-07-13',4,'I stayed here during a recent business trip to NYC. I prioritized location and price over other amenities. This apartment is close to Times Square and all of Midtown, making it convenient for my business trip. It s awkward to have the toilet down the hall, but the place is clean and quiet.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('wcc113',4549,'2017-07-23',5,'I had a wonderful stay at Luiz s!  Everything is as was described.  Centrally located, very quiet, clean... exactly what I needed!  I was surprised by how spacious the room was.  The loft bed really contributes to the feeling of having a nice sized room.  I am beyond pleased with my stay.  I would absolutely stay here again.  Thank you, Luiz!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('penatibus7389',1571,'2016-07-04',5,'This place was just as advertised, It was central to everywhere I wanted to be. Perfect for those who are just needing a place to crash in the evenings and get ready in the mornings. The bathroom is small, but large mirrors are provided in the room which was super helpful for getting ready in the morning. Absolutely a great value, and you get to live like a local!',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('in3395',2653,'2016-01-08',5,'Great location, excellent friendly host, efficient communicator. As mentioned in other reviews the facilities are small but clean and all that is required for me.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sodales69101',1088,'2020-03-22',5,'I visited New York to see Billy Joel in concert and needed a place to stay that wasn t too far from Madison Square Garden.  Luiz s place fit everything I was looking for.I was to check in earlier, but there were problems with my initial flight from Chicago to New York.  I arrived later than expected, about midnight ET, and kept Luiz knowing where I was after my flight landed.  I arrived at his place at 1 AM ET, and Luiz still met me, asked how I was doing, and gave the keys.  He was nice and patient with me the entire time.His place is as the pictures describe.  A room with a loft bed and small couch underneath it.  There are a lot of restaurants nearby, so you will not go hungry.  The subway is very close, with the 42nd Street-Port Authority station a few blocks up the road.  Times Square is nearly along with Madison Square Garden and the Empire State Building.I would definitely stay at his place again if the opportunity presented itself.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('www112',4080,'2021-08-27',5,'wonderful, quite, well positioned place.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('orci23113',1064,'2016-11-21',4,'Incredibly well priced location that is super close to the Javit s convention center. Lots of restaurants nearby and very convenient. Loved the trip and works well for single traveler looking to save some money. His small apartment is remarkably well stocked and he has thought of all things a business traveler might need like an iron / toiletries / internet etc. The check in / ot was simple as well.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('dictumst76178',3265,'2017-11-22',5,'High quality space for budget traveler.  Clean and well cared for place and great location.  Platform bed and small shower and small privaye hall toilet were not a problem for me at allGreat value for someone like me. Who wants clean and private place to stay wirhout breaking the bank.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elit9486',3214,'2018-03-22',5,'good location',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quisque750',50,'2020-07-22',4,'Everything was great and as expected. Especially for the price. Luis was very accommodating and patient as he waited for me to get to the place late at night. Will definitely use again when I am in town.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eget5868',2386,'2020-01-05',5,'Best location!.. In the heart of time square and Madison square garden. Room was quiet and I slept well every night. Tv has movie channels which was awesome at the end of the day while resting after a tour in the city. Wifi was available so I was able to upload NYC pics immediately thru FB and IG. I would definitely book to this place again when I return to NY!',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vestibulum0126',2114,'2021-01-19',5,'It s a very lovely and comfortable room. Also very safe and quite. Walk to Time Square only need 5mins. I love it!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pellentesque33136',1281,'2021-06-15',4,'Luiz place was nice and clean!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('augue8191',3023,'2017-04-07',5,'I loved staying here and hope to stay here again. I just sent a friend a link to this page because I recommended this place to him and now he wants to stay here too.  The location was within a 15 minute walk of every Broadway show I booked. The price is amazing (about 1/3 of what my friend paid at a hotel one block away).  I didn t meet Luiz, but his place was clean and comfortable. I did meet Marcio who showed me around and was very helpful. I wish I had asked all my questions while Marcio was there (I had a little trouble finding towels, shampoo, where to take the trash out once I was on my own). I believe usually Luiz would be very easy to reach, but he had an illness while I was a guest so I didn t get all my questions answered as quickly as I would have if he had been well.  Now I ll be mentioning some things that I didn t mind, but I feel if I had certain friends with me--they wouldn t have liked these elements. I thought it gave me a real experience of NYC as a local. I wasn t sheltered from the real NYC in a touristy hotel.  1) Twice in the mornings, I had to knock on the front door of the building from the inside to get out because of inebriated gentlemen sitting on the steps. They were kind men who moved when I knocked, but I could see how some might find this disconcerting.  2) There is construction right outside the windows of the larger bedroom ( (Website hidden by Airbnb) . Construction is supposed to happen 8a-4p, but it started earlier while I was there. I didn t mind as I m an early riser but some people might.  3) The bathing room is tiny and right off the kitchen. If you re inside it with the door shut, it s a bit challenging to robe/disrobe and the water temperature wasn t consistent in the mornings (when I assume the other residents are also showering).  AirBnB commercials aren t kidding when they say you ll live like a local. I loved it.  If Luiz is open to it, I d be interesting in renting both bedrooms next time. I d have a friend stay with me and it wouldn t be as awkward to use the bathing room. I could walk from my bedroom to the bathing room in a towel or underwear and not have to change in the cramped space of the bathing room. Walking from room to room in a towel/underwear can be awkward if you don t know the person staying in the other bedroom.  I don t find the above things negative, but I think those who might find them negative would want to know about them.  Luiz was generous and kind when I asked to check out later. It worked out that he didn t have another renter right away. Thanks, Luiz, for making your place available. I enjoyed staying there and hope to again.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('erat1120',1893,'2019-04-27',5,'I recommend this apartment!  Great location, clean, and all the space you need for a stay in NYC for a fair low price. Hosts kept in touch with me, met me when I arrived, and even carried my heavy bag up the stairs. They alerted me that the other tenant was arriving so I would know and not be alarmed. I felt safe, and the bathroom being outside and down the hallway did not bother me at all.  I will definitely rent from Luis again!',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('morbi7160',4985,'2017-09-16',5,'Everything was excellent. The place was cozy, nice little kitchen. The bed is loft style, above the couch, and there is a large screen with movies etc...available above the bed. The toilet is outside the apt and down the hall. It was convenient and easy to stay there.mthanks Luiz and Marco!',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut97174',2991,'2018-01-10',5,'I had a great week at Luiz s apartment. I was in town for work and it was exactly where I needed it to be (short walk to Javits) at a great price. The room was large, the apartment as a whole impeccably clean, and very comfortable. Luiz was great to deal with, very communicative and flexible. I would highly recommend this for anyone looking for a good deal.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede63105',2016,'2018-10-12',5,'Cleber is a very nice guy , flexible and let you feel welcome , the condo is very clean and the bad is comfortable ,location is excellent ! Close to time square and subways stations .I have spent 6 days in NY and I had no problem staying in Claber s condo.Thanks Cleber !I hope to stay at your place again next time I came to NY',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('magna6451',2367,'2020-04-10',4,'Was a awesome stay in the city. The location is truly amazing and very safe area. It was very clean and at a awesome price point. Was down in the city for photo expo and it was just about a 5 min walk away from the Jarvis center.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl43160',4121,'2019-07-18',4,'Luiz is an awesome host!! He stayed in contact with me before my stay and throughout.  He helped me out on my last day, and is a really genuinely nice guy.  The apartment is adorable, and the loft bed was so much fun!  It was so close to Times Square, but very quiet so I could get a good night s sleep.  This was my first ever trip to NYC, and this place was the perfect location.  I did not ever feel unsafe, and the apartment is secure.  I will definitely stay here again!!',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo87170',445,'2020-07-28',5,'I enjoyed my time at Luiz s place. The pictures were accurate (the couch has been replaced with a newer one). Great location!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('tempus72169',912,'2017-06-27',3,'This location was better than described! It was really was the perfect location for EVERYTHING that I needed. My stay was over a week, and it really felt like my own little apartment. I oriented very quickly and felt like a New Yorker.  Luiz is such a perfect host. Very accommodating and kind. He was there if you needed something but left you be otherwise. I will definitely stay here EVERY time I m in nyc. <3',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('in3395',546,'2019-05-20',5,'The trip which lived in Luiz s place is wonderful. I like the bedroom design and the bathroom is a little small but already enough for me. The best thing is the location is great and that helped me to save a lot of times. Overall, I like it.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('viverra74104',2501,'2017-11-09',5,'It was exactly what I needed! Super comfortable room. Cozy. Warm. Clean! The host, very polite. Saw him when I went and then when I left. The only thing is the restroom is outside of apt. But it is private. Convenient location. Perfect price. Thanks so much!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et65112',3630,'2021-06-30',4,'Great room. Clean and great value, plenty of space.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('viverra9531',4849,'2020-06-22',5,'My week here was really great. Cleber was awesome, and very helpful throughout the process. The location was unbelievable for the price - pretty short walk to Broadway and Times Square. I highly recommended this place!',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede63105',2288,'2022-02-19',5,'Cleber was amazing and allowed me early check in and was so accomodating.. I wish he had properties everywhere. I would always stay at his place. Best experience and great price.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut1923',4771,'2021-09-09',4,'Stayed at Cleber s apartment again for 4 days last month.  This time he was out of town, but his friend was there to meet me and check me in/out (he knew who I was when I showed up earlier than expected).  I was in the larger room with the loft bed; very neat and comfortable.  My stay was just as good as last year, and I ll come here on my visits to NYC in the future if there s room.  Thanks again, Cleber, and hope to see you next time!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('aenean2690',848,'2020-11-23',5,'Another great stay! The room was great. Bed super comfy, clean and soft sheets, great quality towel.  Drawers to use and a surprising amount of space with the lofted bed. Very clean space - amazing location just minutes from Port Authority and Times Square and TONS of great restaurants and bars near by. Small bathroom but very clean.  Bathroom down the hall is different but not an issue. For the price and convenience, can not be beat!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('penatibus528',730,'2020-03-28',5,'Its a great place to stay I really enjoyed to stay here. Cheap, clean and very well located',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et4430',1960,'2021-12-05',4,'Perfect location and Cleber is a perfect host!  The apartment was spotless and charming.  The bed was very comfortable, as was the whole apartment (not counting the toilet!).  Right next door to a small convenience shop and Irish pub; the location is on restaurant row.  Down the street from the Port Authority - everything you want to do in walking distance.  Cleber was very responsive to all my questions and requests.  Ladies, don t forget to pack your own hair dryer - this is important!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nunc5158',779,'2022-02-12',5,'Cleber was very communicative contacting me via email and text prior to my arrival.  The location was perfect for my purpose of visiting NYC showing in the Javitts two blocks away.  The apartment was very clean, the bed comfortable and the towels soft.   Right out the front door is a mass of restaurants and eateries, and New York life.  Staying here is a no brainer for the price, location and peace of mind knowing Cleber is a good guy, apartment very acceptable and totally convenient.  Already booked for my next trip in January!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vulputate545',4164,'2020-09-19',5,'I had a great time staying with Cleber. He was very helpful in providing information about stuff to do in the area and the shower and room were very clean. Best of all, the AC was strong and worked very well, which was an absolute necessity given the 95+ degree temperatures in NYC at the time. As some noted, the facilities are small, but they get the job done so I can go back out and explore the city. And the price is unbeatable. Definitely recommend it to anyone who wants to explore the city (only a few blocks from Times Square).',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('integer6474',1562,'2017-02-06',5,'Cleber was a great host! The Apartment is clean and quiet. Location is ideal to get anywhere in Manhattan. I will definitely be asking to stay again, or referring peeps to Cleber. This is a great deal!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('rutrum7621',1089,'2020-03-11',5,'This is a great place to crash that is convenient to everywhere I needed to be (Times Square, Chelsea, W Vill, etc.). As a former NYC resident I appreciated the unique set up of the apt (toilet down the hall, tiny shower, etc.), but for me it s not a problem since I m out and about and only used the apt. as a crash pad. Cleber is a great host because he s there when he says he ll be there, greets you, gives you the lowdown....then he s gone! ha haha Only used this place because my regular place where i stay for free was not available. This is an ideal alternative I will remember for future trips (I come to NYC about once a month).',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('in54195',1040,'2021-04-19',5,'I met Gisela who was there cleaning the apartment and getting everything set while Cleber was away. The apartment was perfect! Amazing location, very comfortable bed, lots of room, and impeccably clean! Gisela was also an amazing person and even bought some coffee before she turned the apartment over. I had a great time, and I d definitely stay there again!',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('in54195',2605,'2017-11-19',5,'First time using airbnb.com, great experience!!! Thanks Cleber!! Nice bedroom and clean place. Very helpful host. Location is perfect!!! Short walk from port authority and Time square. Thanks again!',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('consequat2734',1677,'2018-11-01',4,'Great location - convenient walking distance to Times Square, many local restaurants, the Skyline and the Metro.  Bus connections excellent to Lincoln Center.  Very clean and functional apartment.  Only drawbacks are that the guest room is small and the (private) toilet is down the hall - a bit of a pain if you have to get up in the night.   Cleber was out of town, but Gisela and Cindy handled the checkin and get me set up.  Would definately stay here again. Great place to stay for one person!',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl36148',3041,'2021-11-09',5,'My friend and I had a great time in NY and Cleber s apartment was very conveniently located with Times square a couple of blocks away and restaurants and bars just down the street. The flat was clean, comfortable and funky. Check in was very easy with Gisella being super helpful and accommodating. I would recommend CLeber s apartment to anyone looking for a place to stay in NY. Thanks!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae9127',842,'2019-12-03',5,'The location is awesome. Subway stations and bus terminal are within 5 to 10 minutes  walk. The apartment is very close to Time Square and all the other hotspots in NYC, so I walked a lot instead of taking public transportations. Moreover, Cleber is such a hospitable host. He gave me a lot of suggestions about traveling and shopping. The bedroom, bathroom, and restroom are clean. The decoration is elegant. If I revisit NYC in the future, I will definitely choose here next time!',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('justo40189',1912,'2021-01-16',4,'Cleber is a great guy, with a fantastic apt!  Located just steps from Time Square, you ve got access to the heart of Manhattan, and you can jump on a subway in any direction. Most affordable apt in this area.  Cleber is a very accommodating host, and keeps a very clean and well organized place.  I highly recommend staying at Cleber s place!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede50164',1933,'2018-09-10',5,'Good room, excellent location. Thoroughly enjoyed the stay. Highly recommended!',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ullamcorper075',4412,'2016-09-25',5,'The room was very clean with a closet and hangers. Also provided was free wifi, a TV and free use of the kitchen. Cleber was a great host, very friendly and a joy to chat with. He provided a towel and an extra blanket. Would recommend this room to anyone',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('luctus0123',4574,'2019-03-01',5,'It s a great location, for sure. Host is very nice and accommodating. As it says in the description, there is a private toilet but it s not in the apartment, so you have to walk down the hall to use it. Which is fine, unless you need to get up in the middle of the nightâ€¦Â stumbling down a brightly lit hall, fumbling with the lock on the door to go to the bathroom isn t my favorite thing to do at 4am. BUT, given the price for a clean bed in a safe apartment in a great location in New York City, it s hard to argue!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('consequat4359',3678,'2017-08-03',4,'The host canceled my reservation 29 days before arrival.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('mi5344',2685,'2018-11-27',5,'I had one of my colleagues stay with Cleber (I already had an another place lined up). My colleague told me that Cleber is very friendly and that his place is nice and clean. He also said that he would like to stay there again whenever he has an opening while we are in NYC.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam39115',828,'2022-01-18',5,'Cleber s apartment is amazingly well located, just few from the heart of Times Square and all the subway lines (A, C, E, N, Q, R, W, S, 1, 2, 3, 7 and 9). If you are coming from JFK, LaGuardia or Newark Airports, just take the shuttle bus to Port Authority Bus Terminal and walk four short blocks to get to his place. Despite this proximity with this evermoving touristic center, the place is very quiet. Cleber is a very nice, polite, helpful and discreet host. For sure I will stay at his place on my next trip to NYC!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('viverra76180',4813,'2020-08-12',4,'He was really a nice guy. I was not in the home much. But when I was, he was great. I would stay again. Justin',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nulla23161',1527,'2016-06-16',5,'Cleber! Muito obrigado! This guy is the bomb! I will definitely stay back at this place next time!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('penatibus528',2859,'2020-01-22',5,'This room is great for one person. The host is charming and warm. I read the ad wrong and was under the assumption that I would be renting a small apt. and not just a room in somebody s apt.-Totally my fault. The apt. is very clean and well taken care of.It s very convenient to get around. More than one person would be very difficult.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede82145',1044,'2018-04-18',5,'Cleber was a down to earth nice guy. Very clean and giving. Offered me coffee & food graciously. Location of unit is very good. Close to E train. 42nd St transfers to almost all subway trains. Located on 2nd floor, easy to get to... quiet too. Lots of eat options. I liked the Thai food place nearby. I really liked my private flat screen TV for local news & weather.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit21153',2698,'2020-06-02',5,'Cleber is a good and friendly host. And the location is very good - it s close to everything, though Midtown West is not exactly my favorite place in the world.  Cleber advertises this, so there s no surprise, but  you should be fully aware of the quirks of his place: the toilet is not in the same room as the shower (and indeed, is outside the apartment), and the AC didn t work when I was there.  All in all, a fair price for an okay apartment in a good location with a nice host.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl43160',1894,'2020-12-31',4,'Indeed best location in NYC.  Walking distance to everything, clean place and host very friendly. I found this place for my female friends. They were delighted about the place and also about Cleber, the host, who made them feel very welcomed.  You have Times Square less than 5 minutes walk. All the trains get you close to the apartment.   Definitely will recommend this place to anyone coming to NY.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ucc15',2926,'2016-08-26',5,'Room in the heart of New York for an unbeatable price.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('augue90110',707,'2016-03-26',5,'The flat is clean and there is anything you ll need for a short stay, even if the main room is more little than the pictures shows.The neighborhood can appear as not safe for a lonely  woman ( many hobos in the streets around) but all was ok for me.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('montes9279',3562,'2019-08-02',4,'Very welcoming person, takes care of everything.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('accumsan84173',4202,'2019-08-23',5,'Excelent location and the best you could get for the price.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam10149',1048,'2020-06-15',5,'The location is amazing and Francisco and Luiz are very nice. The building is very old, bathtub was clogged. Its a good place for a couple of days!!',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit96122',1892,'2018-05-26',4,'It is located in a fantastic part of NYC, very close to lots of excellent landmarks, restaurants and shopping. The room is well decorated and very cosy during the cold winter weather. The bathroom is very small and awkward, and the toilet is outside in the hall and also very small, so would not suit someone who is very tall or large. That said, it was fine for me, and the price and location are unbeatable. Michelle was wonderful during the checkin, even though I was delayed from the airport and had to go straight to a meeting in another part of town.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nunc5158',543,'2016-11-08',5,'This space is perfect for solo travellers, very close to Times Square and subway! Space as advertised room is clean, shower is quite small and the toilet is in the hallway in a small space. But perfect for a short trip to the city.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elementum23143',337,'2020-01-23',5,'The best thing about this place is no doubt the location! Super convenient and walking distance to lots of cool places in Manhattan. The apartment is not the best but for the price it s okay. Beware the toilet is located in the hallway outside the apartment, only the shower is in the apartment itself. Also, Luiz himself did not respond to me on airbnb, but a few days before I arrived I got in touch with someone who then checked me in, so it worked out okay. Overall fairly good and in line with what you can expect for this price in Manhattan.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sed6042',1655,'2017-07-14',4,'Amazing location clean and friendly people',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('rhoncus2633',3951,'2019-11-10',5,'The best',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae1580',1225,'2021-07-23',5,'Great location. Enough space in the apartment. Quirky bathroom facilities. Would recommend for young travellers only.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo87170',1465,'2016-08-03',4,'Great stay - good communication. Place is small but fantastic location',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ultrices32193',4736,'2021-06-17',5,'If you happen to be a person who gets up through the night to go to the washroom, this place is perhaps not for you as you need to exit the unit and go down the hall, unlock the bathroom door to access the toilet and do your deeds. The washroom in the unit has a tiny sink and bathtub/shower only which is accessed by going up one step for the step for the sink and another for the tub. Access would be difficult for people with mobility issues or who are a tad overweight. The medicine chest above the sink sticks out so that it is almost impossible to spit out into the sink after washing teeth. I used my hand to cup the liquids to avoid spitting in the floor.,',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et65112',505,'2019-07-26',5,'Arranged on my sons behalf for his visit to NY. All good, everything you need to know in Luiz s details and the reviews.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam2176',513,'2016-01-25',5,'The location is excellent! It is a few blocks from the subways; there is a grocery store and good restaurants nearby. The place is as described. Luiz is a helpful and accommodating host. He shares his home with his guests, where he is both helpful and professional.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('consequat2734',86,'2018-12-06',4,'The apartment is small as described in the ad but very near to Times Square and Broadway. This is definitely a deal for solo travelers',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('cycy23',2359,'2016-01-04',5,'centrally located ,got everything needed . Luiz was very responsive and helpful',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('justo40189',4591,'2016-03-16',5,'This was my second time staying in Luiz s apartment. Everything is exactly as described. The bed is very comfortable and there is a nice TV with Netflix ect. Location is fantastic for most touristy activities. I would absolutely stay here again in the future.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quisque750',4879,'2019-10-21',4,'Well located',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('mi5344',2130,'2017-04-29',5,'The perfect Place to stay in Midtown Manhattan!',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('curabitur44172',4615,'2018-09-16',5,'Luiz was very responsive and helpful for our stay. Unfortunately it wasnt overly clear that the apartment doesnt have a bathroom inside at all, you have to go out into the hallway and unlock it with a key which was an uncomfortable experience. Overall fine although we did have one extra guest and the extra charge was quite expensive for the value and size of the apartment but we appreciate him accomodating us at short notice. Location was great for getting around and for getting to the airport.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('massa9626',758,'2020-11-25',5,'Location was excellent and the room was very clean and nice. It was the same as in pictures. I would definitely recommend this place as it was clean, comfortable and I felt like home.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae3652',1581,'2016-07-09',5,'Superb location close to Times Square Madison Square garden Grand Central station, the High Line, the Vessel and the Empire State Building. I like walking and found it easy to stroll to Central Park too. Spotlessly clean with lots of amenities. Good value for such well located accommodation.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vulputate545',3354,'2021-06-13',4,'Room was decent however shower room and toilet are incredibly tiny.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede20152',4580,'2018-06-19',5,'Great location, nicely decorated and easy check in. The flat and separate toilet are shared by another airbnb tenant, though. The separate toilet did not bother me during my stay.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut42159',2981,'2020-05-24',5,'I didn t had opportunity to meet him, but he provided a clean bedroom and bathroom. The room itself is comfortable. apartment is at a convenient location',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nulla91184',3531,'2019-07-06',4,'Waking distance or a short subway ride to nearly everywhere you want to be in NYC.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede82145',3664,'2019-02-25',5,'Very good location near Times Square!',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sodales69101',1071,'2018-10-25',5,'A very nice and decent place!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae1580',1605,'2019-07-29',4,'The stay at Luiz place was really great. The directions to his apartment from JFK airport worked flawlessly and the description of the apartment itself is well depicted. The apartment was really clean and the location is in walking distance to a lot of the new tourist attractions (The Vessel, Hudson Yards, Highline, Times Square, etc.), plus close to the NY subway.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ucc15',4684,'2017-06-28',5,'Room is quite good, shower/basin and toilets are an inconvenience if larger than average in height or weight',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('suscipit47120',2886,'2017-12-14',5,'Great location only a 10 minute walk to time square',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nonummy2158',4866,'2017-07-30',5,'Location is fantastic. There is some construction work happening near by but if you re like me and can sleep through anything, then it s not an issue.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eu25190',995,'2019-05-22',5,'Small but clean as described. Great location',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et4755',3055,'2022-02-26',5,'I had travel problems in the run up to my stay but Luiz was able to work round my issues and accommodate. Always got back to me quickly any time I got in touch. The apartment itself is in a great location just 5 minutes away from Times Square yet it still quiet.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pellentesque33136',4989,'2017-04-28',4,'Great apartment and a great location for a short stay in New York. Room was nice and bed comfortable. Would stay again!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('velit13144',800,'2019-06-19',5,'Luiz was not there but the person is charge was very nice, the room is large with Netflix included. The only â€œbadâ€ thing is that the bathroom is outside the apartment, but in general is an excellent place to stay a couple days while visiting NYC.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eu25190',278,'2020-11-15',5,'The host canceled this reservation 52 days before arrival. This is an automated posting.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('fusce2549',3136,'2017-08-06',4,'Perfect place for a few nights in New York! Big TV in the room with access to Netflix. Host was very responsive to messages! From the listing description I thought the apartment was going to be in the heart of Times Square but it was actually about a 10 min walk away. Despite this, still a very central, good location. Bathroom and toilet a bit small, but totally workable. Overall would recommend :)',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('erat89150',3910,'2016-02-24',5,'Everything ok! good location and he was helpful with me. ',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nascetur76125',2598,'2017-08-21',5,'Recommend it for people that will not spend much time in apartment. It is near to most touristic areas and guys keep place clean. Problems that I have: The place is really small, so its not really comfortable. The heating of the bedroom was not working and they werent able to fix it during my stay, even they know of the problem before I arrived, and It was really cold because was snowing outside.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('in63197',4274,'2019-03-03',4,'Had a great short stay at Luizs apartment. Great location! Only a short 5 minute walk to Times Square and major subways! The toilet is seperate to the apartment but I didnt find it to be an issue. Overall a good stay.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('semper2147',3818,'2016-02-06',5,'The location is great! Perfect for exploring the night time of the city centre.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ucc26',2791,'2017-07-14',5,'Very nice location and warm welcome by the owner.Very good for the price ! Very clean. Just take some good winter clothes for the night because the small electric heater is not suitable to warm up the room.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('tempor6567',854,'2016-08-10',5,'I m not sure what happened or why it took so long to remedy but I arrived for my three day stay in NYC to signs on the wall informing me that there was no heat or hot water. The situation was not remedied during my stay and unfortunately for them, on my last night there a new guest was entering the second room and I m not sure if they were informed either as I would have changed my mind that s for sure. They were asleep by the time I got back however.Judging from the other reviews this seems to be abnormal but I can only write a review based on my own experiences.  I wish it had been otherwise as the unit, while smaller than I expected, was in a great location and otherwise a good value.If you do stay there I recommend the pub Skallywags downstairs.  A friendly watering hole.  And warm.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('cubilia59166',4145,'2018-05-11',5,'Great place! A gem in manhattan. Easy access from JFK and the helpful communication from Luiz was spot on. Defo stay again! Highly recommend.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('velit8725',4580,'2020-07-16',5,'Luiz was a fantastic host. He was contactable about any questions relating to my stay. He is incredibly pleasant and everything is as described.The place was recently renovated so everything is new and fresh. There is a lovely TV and bed. Location couldn t be better. It is in the center of everything. I would absolutely stay here again.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('posuere8385',1278,'2019-05-04',4,'Great location, lovely room, 10min walk to time square, 20min walk to Central Park. Host is lovely as well!Will stay again',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nulla56102',894,'2019-03-01',4,'Great spot! Right by Midtown, with easy access to the Upper West Side, Downtown, and even a short-ish walk to Grand Central. The place is very quiet, only on my last day did I see another person in the hallway, and someone in the other attached AirBNB property. A welcome relief from the hustle and bustle out on the streets :)',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eu1673',1564,'2017-03-20',5,'Cozy space located in a good location. A good choice for the solo traveler',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('id3571',783,'2020-03-06',3,'Great value. Nice and quiet place, very central. AC in the summer was much appreciated.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('augue8191',1152,'2016-03-09',5,'Great place, clean, everything you need and in a great location for everything central in manhattan. Thanks!',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo87170',2796,'2018-10-22',5,'Nice, small space in a very convenient location and the host was very responsive.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elementum51171',2198,'2021-07-02',4,'Luiz s place was a great value for the money. It was a nice room in a good location close to Times Square. The apartment was functional and the bed was comfy.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('rutrum7621',2506,'2017-05-28',5,'I give 5 out of 5 stars for the location. For anything else I will not give more than 1 star.I do not recommend this place.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut97174',72,'2021-02-23',5,'Amazing value since accommodation in NYC is ridiculously expensive. The place is very close to Times Square and the theatre district. Room was large and clean. It did get really hot up on the loft bed even with the a/c on since hot air goes up, room probably could do with a ceiling fan. Shower water pressure was a bit bad and I sometimes couldnt get hot water running so had to take a cold shower. Toilet being outside is a bit of a pain but it all worked fine. All in all, this is a good place to stay, being in manhattan and not going to break your bank.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('penatibus7389',597,'2021-03-28',4,'The place is strategically located in Manhattan and is easily a great choice to those who prefer to be close to where the hustle and bustle are in the city. Tony, who helps familiarise occupants to the place, is very helpful and responsive through SMS to my queries.It is advisable that occupants keep the shower room unlocked to avoid accidental lock outs. Keep your keys with you all the time.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sed91175',582,'2017-08-05',5,'The room is one of two in a second floor apartment, located 2 minutes walk away from Port Authority bus station and 5-10 minutes from the theatre district. Despite its central location, the place is generally quiet and the other guest was barely noticeable. The bedroom itself was spacious thanks to the loft layout, and the bed and sheets were amazingly comfortable! The entire place is extremely clean and tidy and the hosts are very hospitable and responsive.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('dapibus9796',1102,'2018-03-25',5,'I really enjoyed staying at Luiz  apartment! The best thing about it is definitely the location in the center of manhatten. Also, it is very clean and the check-in and check-out was very easy! The apartment consists of two bedrooms which are rented separately, means you share the living room and bathroom with another person. But that s totally okay because if you don t want to meet the other person you can stay in your bedroom which is big enough. The only negative point is that the bathroom is very small but it s okay.',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('non93107',3654,'2019-01-23',4,'very good location for being close to New York attractions and transport. Luiz will respond and be very accomodating in ensuring your stay is a comfortable one.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quisque750',1241,'2019-10-28',5,'Place is just as advertized. Central location, close to Penn Station and Times Square. Cozy and comfortable. Plenty of restaurants and shops close by. Would stay here again.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ut35181',2007,'2016-05-22',5,'Although I didn t meet Luiz, I met his friend Tony who was helpful and available via text should I have any queries or concerns. As some other reviewers mentioned, neither Luiz nor Tony stay at the apartment, only the guests do.The room is pretty spacious and clean, and they also provided towels for my stay, which I think was a nice touch. The kitchen is a decent size and clean, plus having access to its amenities makes any trip cheaper.The bathroom is really small and the water pressure for the shower is a bit low, so if you have long hair like me you might be in there for a while. Also pointed out in the room posting is the fact that the toilet is outside the apartment, which can be inconvenient. But it was clean, although a bit cramped.The location of the apartment is very good and I was able to walk pretty much anywhere in Midtown or just get the Subway two blocks away.If you re travelling by yourself and don t mind the toilet issue, I d say this place is ideal. I d stay there again if ever back in NYC.',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('semper2147',3737,'2021-04-29',5,'This was my second stay at Luizs place. It was a clean and quiet room and a good bet for an authentic apartment close to Times Square.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam39115',2944,'2017-09-22',5,'Luiz and his place are great. Would always come back :)',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et4430',4113,'2019-08-10',4,'Location is central to the city and near to night life. If you are planning to spend most of the time in midtown, this is a great place to stay. I found it slightly pricey (but it may be midtown standard). Bathroom is very small in size and to access the toilet you need to go to hallway (outside apartment). The toilet is also very small and you need to unlock and lock it back when you use it. It is unconvineint but not a deal breaker.',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('justo40189',3896,'2017-03-10',5,'Really good location close to time square. The neighbourhood felt safe. There was some noise from construction work outside my bedroom window but it didnt bother me much. The room was big and spacious and the bed was comfortable. Over all a pretty good place to stay. And Luiz was a very nice host :)',7);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nunc61133',3481,'2016-11-29',5,'Great place to stay near Time Square!The apartment is kind of small with toilet in the hallway, but it s so convenient to go everywhere and hangout late!Great experience!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eu1673',4910,'2017-10-12',4,'Luiz place is always amazing.  I always feel right at home.   It has everything you need.  So close to everything, trains, bus s and on the doorstep of Times Square!   My second time in NY and both at Luiz.   I would stay there again in a heart beat !!   Thanks Luiz !!',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elit9486',4498,'2021-04-18',5,'Absolute perfect location, minutes away from fabulous restaurants, Times Square and central for getting around. I was nervous about sharing with a stranger - however having bedroom locks was added security. The loft bed was so comfortable, linen beautifully laundered including the towel. Spotlessly clean and suprisingly large space in the room. I felt like I was constantly asking Luiz questions however he promptly replied patiently to each. Would highly recommend staying here and a bargain for the price and location.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('fusce2549',596,'2018-05-07',5,'Absolutely fabulous, very close to time sq and theatre district, easy to find, and easy to navigate away from here. A perfect host with great communication, very accommodating when my flight was delayed and I had to miss a night. Would stay here again in a heartbeat.',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit22151',672,'2017-04-18',4,'It was a great experience. The place was clean and bed was very comfortable. And great location, close to Time Square and all of Midtown. I did many things only on foot. I would like stay again.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('yyy19',1149,'2021-10-14',5,'The best location and great host! You are 10min (aprox) walking distance from Times Square, and close to many of NY main attractions. A couple of things: The bed was on top of a small set of stairs, so it might not be very accessible for some people. The toilet is outside of the apartment and very small (the shower is inside the apartment though). If you are ok with these two things, then you ll have a great time. Everything else was as described so I would definitely recommend it.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('faucibus16134',3263,'2022-02-04',5,'Luiz  place was super close to all the action of NYC, the place was clean, I stayed in the bunk room and it was really big and the air con was great. Awesome value for money and I d definitely stay again!',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae9127',3056,'2018-07-31',5,'Very kind. It is a suitable place for New York for the first time',23);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elementum5887',2809,'2018-12-27',4,'All good :)',20);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('amet7277',2901,'2019-04-24',5,'Luiz s place is really well located and really worth it for the price you re paying. The room is big. It was a sofa-bed on which I was able to work. The mattress and pillows are really, really good which made me sleep really well. The internet is also good, which made my work really smooth.Only thing that I didn t expect was that the bathroom and toilet are really small, but I ignored that because of the price I was paying.Luis is an awesome host. He helped me check in and answered all my questions. I m definitely staying at his place again when I come back to NYC.',15);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl1470',582,'2021-08-08',5,'Luiz is an amazing person, I had easy contact with him from check in to check out. Great location in NY, close to public transport and Time Square, I did many things only on foot due to great location. I recommend it for sure.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('interdum2176',954,'2018-01-02',4,'Awesome apartment in a centered location. Very well designed, nice and cool during humid days.Luiz previred everything I need and was very kind and responsieve.Thank you Luiz!',27);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vulputate545',116,'2019-01-22',5,'I had absolutely no problem communicating with Luiz throughout my trip in NY! He was really nice and considerate. The apartment was accurate as the online pictures show. The only problem for me is that both the bathroom and the shared toilet are pretty small.',18);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('lacinia30117',764,'2019-05-29',5,'It s a really nice cosy private place. I enjoyed living here.',22);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('elementum5887',3987,'2018-01-22',5,'I booked the property for my traveling friend, he said that the place was clean, well maintained, and Luiz was extremely helpful and friendly. Would recommend to others!',27);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('mi8963',4634,'2016-09-12',5,'This place was perfect for me as I wanted to be in Manhattan for a nearby event. Luiz s place is very clean and the pictures are accurate. A small thing in the building was fixed and remedied right away when brought to Luiz s attention. I would recommend!',11);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('amet7277',1209,'2017-08-14',4,'Right next to Time Square and loads of eating options all around. Good place to stay.',25);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('suscipit47120',1350,'2021-02-02',5,'It s close to Times Square, and bed  was so comfortable.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam39115',4824,'2019-12-13',5,'Placed in a very central location, the apartment is cozy, clean and well equipped.Only con: the bathroom and the toilet room (5 mt from the apartment, in the aisle) are both small, but serve their purpose.',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede50164',3050,'2016-12-24',4,'Great location. Room is pretty and clean. Bathroom is outside of the appartment, and shared with the guest from the other room.',21);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('aenean67124',60,'2018-05-09',5,'Great place! Great location. Great host! A nice clean apartment. True to pictures. Thanks Luiz. Definitely recommend! ',28);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('id8072',2289,'2020-09-27',5,'Everything worked out perfectly, Luiz is a great, flexible host and very welcoming! Good neighbourhood to explore NYC!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('cycy23',4572,'2017-03-08',4,'This airbnb has a very good location with many public transportation around, so you can get anywhere really quick. Bathroom was very small and a little bit smelly (no windows). The bed was very comfortable, but if you have a light sleep like I do, there are a few things you should be aware of: You can hear everything though the wall (there is another airbnb roommate in the apartment, who you share the bathroom and toilet with). The neighborhood is very busy on weekend nights, you can hear cars, music etc. There is a huge construction site right outside the room, and they start to work early in the morning on weekdays. Communication with Luiz was all ok, though he was not there when I checked in but his friend Carol, who was also very responsive thoughout the stay. All in all ok for a short stay.',22);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nibh7765',1398,'2019-08-19',5,'Luiz was very pleasant and welcoming. I loved the room, it was clean and the bed was amazing. I would definitely come back.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('montes9279',1420,'2017-04-29',5,'Well located place to get to know the city. Great attention from the host.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vitae3652',4835,'2018-02-18',4,'Everything was good! The location is perfect!',5);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ligula35188',4611,'2019-09-05',5,'This room couldn t better! I ve felt cozy during my stay. I ll recommand others who wanna find good place to bnb.',13);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sapien4153',2715,'2017-09-07',5,'Luiz s place is a good choice if you want to be close to Times Square, but don t want the noise. The room is a perfect size for one or two travellers, and located in a quiet building. The shower room and bathroom are very small, but worked just fine. The bed was clean and comfortable. Luiz provided a towel, extra blankets and an umbrella just in case. Overall, I would recommend this place for someone not concerned about luxury, but interested in an authentic budget stay close to lots of sights.',16);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('sit42135',4682,'2019-05-07',4,'Luiz is very nice. Thank you for the apt. the bathroom and toilet is a little small, but it have everything you need.  the location is wonderful, you can walk to many theatre only 10 minutes, don t need take subway. there are two bedroom, only you and another guest. the bed is very very comfortable.  If I come back to NYC, I hope can stay here again.',21);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pellentesque33136',4328,'2022-01-13',5,'Close to time square, bars and restuarants',17);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ligula35188',1926,'2018-08-03',5,'Very nice loft, really cozy and confortable. Good position in silent quartier. Wi-Fi too slow and wc really too little ( at about 5mt from apt.).',23);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('suscipit47120',2022,'2017-06-13',5,'The location of the apartment is really exceptional! The bedroom with the orange wall has an excellent size and a great bed. Also, it s definitely not loud, considering that you re in the middle of Manhattan.On the other hand, I had problems with the heating s system and with the hot water (fault of the boiler of the building), which made it impossible for me to take some showers and made me feel very cold on some nights (the temperature was -15 Â° C in NY and I only had 2 blankets available, so I had to sleep with my snow clothes), and with the lock of the house, which broke - because of that, I had to stay until 1 am involved in the repair, because the owner of the property was not in the city, just like the person he had indicated to be responsible. I also would say that the bathroom is uncomfortably small.Despite this, the cost benefit pays off if you are going to spend a few nights close to everything and do not mind overcoming some uncomfortable mishaps.',26);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('penatibus7389',446,'2018-03-02',4,'Room was quite spacious, cozy and tidy!! Bathroom and toilets are tiny but I find it quite an interesting experience to use. Location is convinient but there is construction work right outside the room while I was here.',16);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('at81162',1436,'2021-01-18',5,'The apartment was exactly as shown on the pictures: clean and tidy. The bed is super comfortable and cozy. Internet was reliable and fast. Neighborhood is safe and close to Broadway theaters, subway stations that can get you to anywhere in Manhattan and walking distance to Times Square.I would recommend the place to other guests. I didn t get to meet Luiz but he was always available via Airbnb.',16);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pellentesque33136',2914,'2018-06-19',5,'The apartment is kind of small, but it has an excellent location. In the neighborhood there are lots of bars, restaurants, stores and almost in front of the apartments there is a supermarket. It has a kitchen, refrigerator and microwave. All the tools for cooking, also some tools as screwdriver and a hair dryer.It s very close from Times Square, Fifth Avenue and other touristic places such as Broadway, Central Park, Madison Square Garden, Empire State Building. You could went to this places walking from the apartment.In the future, I will stay there again.',12);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('convallis2682',629,'2021-04-02',4,'Great location and perfect for sightseeing on foot; I rarely got the metro in the 5 days I stayed. The room was surprisingly spacious and the bed was super comfy. Luiz was very friendly and welcomed me when I arrived.  Would highly recommend!',12);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('accumsan84173',1626,'2019-05-31',5,'Luiz s place was perfect for my short 2 day stay in NYC, being my first time in the city it was great to have transportation and times square in such close proximity. Everything was extremely clean and tidy, and I was always comfortable in the unit. The washroom was a little different being outside the unit but it wasn t a problem at all. I would definitely stay here again and recommend friends to stay as well.',26);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('fusce2549',4143,'2020-07-05',5,'The area,  the location, the hospitality and the way the apartment was presented. Very neat and very tidy with everything you need to accommodate your stay. To top it off it is located in a very accessible area and has a very helpful host.',15);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('faucibus16134',3034,'2016-06-15',5,'Luiz is a great host, very responsive, friendly and helpful. The room and apartment is as described and the location is very good for tourists or even business travelers, as it is right in the heart of Manhattan. Definitely a recommendation!',8);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('proin7639',302,'2018-05-13',5,'The room was exactly as described.  A great location in Hell s Kitchen.  A comfortable bed, and great kitchen facilities.  I really appreciated Luiz s care at providing a great room, meeting me and showing me the ropes.',11);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('amet7277',1334,'2017-02-17',4,'This was a good room at a very good location. Time Square was in walking distance and one would never get bored here. The apartment was in an old building but I got used to it very quickly. Luiz had kept the room and the toilet in super-clean condition. During my four nights here, there was no noise at all. Luiz was a very good host and answered all my questions and needs. I really would like to stay here again if I ever come back to Manhattan!',3);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nulla23161',1269,'2019-09-20',5,'Luiz is friendly and helpful. The bedroom is clean and cozy. Restroom and shower room are clean too, but kind of small.  The price is good.  The location is very convenient.',27);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('pede20152',4069,'2021-07-08',5,'Luiz is quick to response.The location is super convenient. The room is clean and well coordinated.I will come back again!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('mone116',4388,'2020-04-16',4,'I stayed for 2 weeks in Luiz s place and it was a great experience. The location is perfect, everything is just few blocks away and there s a lot of good options to eat in the same street. The room is spacious and since the bed is on the upper level you got plenty of space to put your stuff. The external toilet is a bit weird but you get used to it and I never met with other people in the hallway. Overall it was a good experience and Luiz was available every time I needed him.',28);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('proin9892',702,'2021-02-10',5,'This room is exactly the same as described and pictured. Everything you need is provided, small but cozy and warm. The raised bed makes the room spacious. TV programs look awesome and WiFi connection is stable and fast. Bathroom is just next door, with shampoo and body wash. Although the toilet is not in the room, it is just a few meters away and private. It s not a problem at all. This location is great for people who want to explore the city in the day and night because it s quite central and has good public transport connection. There are many doors on the way to the room so I think it s very safe. Luiz is warm-hearted and always responses to your question. He is also caring the feeling of the people staying here and tries to do his best to be a great host. Thank you Luiz. I had a wonderful staying in NYC.',22);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('eget5868',3052,'2021-10-26',5,'Everything was awesome! Best Location in the Heart of Manhattan, Subway, pups and Restaurants all in the neighbourhood. Perfect to Discover Manhattan and have a Break before you go on. Cozy, clean Appartement. I recommend this to everyone. If you got the chance- go and get it. I loved this neighbourhood and will definitly go back there. Luiz Is a very good Host, he s friendly and if you got a question he will do his best to answer it. Thanks for everything luiz!',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('lobortis43186',1600,'2019-12-14',4,'Luiz was a pleasure to deal with from the moment of booking all the way through to leaving the apartment. He wasn t living onsite at the time, but was there to greet me and show me all the facilities. He is very easy to contact. Sharing the apartment with another traveller is no hassle and you have great privacy. The shower and basin are inside the apartment, and the toilet is only a few steps out on the hallway and is your apartments exclusive use. Don t let this put you off, it s really fine ( and I am usually very fussy). The apartment is spotless, and the room I booked was plenty big enough for me, and my luggage and to be able to do some work the as well. It took me around 10 mins to walk to the Javits centre for a convention, and it s about the same to the middle of Time Square. There are a ton of great places to eat right on your doorstep, and I highly recommend Scallywags the Irish pub next door for a drink and to meet some awesome people. This Partmemt is such a good price  brilliant location, and for the money, hard to beat.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('fusce2549',4302,'2021-12-05',5,'Great stay in fantastic, central location.  Luiz was great and kept in regular contact, clear instructions made getting from the airport to and from the apartment a breeze via subway, and perfect location to base yourself for all the sights and sounds NY has to offer. The mezzanine bed meant the room was spacious with lots of room to spread out bags etc. Bathroom/shower/toilet setup is a bit unusual, but totally workable - given the price, and location, it s a small inconvenience in the scheme of things! As solo female traveller, safety & security always a consideration but happy to report no probs at all. Thanks Luiz for a great stay!',17);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('duis34168',581,'2017-03-28',5,'Best location! SÃºper clean and cozy. The apartment has everything you need! Thank you Luiz!!!',17);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('aenean67124',1040,'2017-05-17',5,'The host canceled this reservation 53 days before arrival. This is an automated posting.',6);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('orci41111',246,'2019-12-11',5,'Luiz was a fantastic host. Very welcoming and Also helped me out on my last night in NYC.I hope to stay there again sometime in the future.location was perfect',13);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('lobortis43186',889,'2021-10-18',5,'Nice apartment, great location :)',10);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('nisl43160',4118,'2017-08-08',4,'Luiz made me feel welcome right away. I loved the room, it was clean and just like on the pictures.  The location is convenient, close to Times Square and other main attractions in New York.  I felt safe and comfortable.  Would book it again ;)',27);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo87170',1110,'2018-04-27',5,'The apartment is comfortable and the neighbourhood is safe and nice.',20);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('lorem1829',2867,'2020-08-03',5,'Luis was a great and considerate host! Very caring and hospitable',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam2176',3999,'2016-09-19',4,'Luis was an excellent host, and went out of his way to accommodate my schedule.  The apartment was exactly as depicted. The loft bed was comfortavle, and the place was clean, tidy, and quiet. Air conditioner was a plus.',25);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('semper2147',4648,'2016-07-27',5,'I had a great stay at New York and Luiz s place! Luiz place is just awesome, which is near to time square and Broadway! I can walk back home after I watched phantom of the opera! And I love the room so much! It s spacious and its great for girl like me who had a lot of stuffs! The bed which is upstairs is super comfortable! And you have a kitchen and bedroom just next to your room. Toilet is out of the room but it s ok for me~ everything was fine and I really enjoy the stay!',9);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('et65112',4667,'2016-08-31',4,'Very good location to travel in the city! The room is spacious, clean and surprisingly quiet in the night. Would strongly recommend to friends whoever need to travel to NYC.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('tristique8035',233,'2022-01-14',5,'I already miss New York! I had a really great time and a big factor to that is Luiz s place. I ve stayed there for 6 nights and I m really glad I did. The room is clean and cozy. There is a huge amount of space to place your things. The shower is inside the apartment, however, the toilet is a few steps outside. But hey, you can t really compare that to the convenience that the place will give you. Luiz s apartment is close to a lot of must see places in NY and to the subway & bus stations too! There s a lot of restaurants and cafes nearby as well. And the most important of all, Luiz is a great host and very accommodating. I will definitely stay at this room again when I go back to New York!',12);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('wcc113',3654,'2016-09-14',5,'Definitely the best location. The apartment is very clean and cozy. Luiz received me with attention and he is a great person. My first experience with airbnb was excellent.',2);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('a83185',1229,'2022-01-28',5,'Thanks for the perfect stay. Cleber offered excellent communication prior to arrival. The room was exactly as described. It was easy to find and really easy to negotiate my way there from JFK using the subway for just 7$. The room and apartment was very clean and the bed was incredibly comfortable. Your sheets are the comfiest I have ever slept in !!  The location is perfect for access to the whole of the city. Thanks for a great stay and I hope to come back !! I would not hesitate to recommend this apartment.  Thanks.',15);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('a22154',4749,'2021-07-26',5,'Luiz s apartment is awesome! It s very clean and cozy. I felt like home! The location is very good as well. It s close to the subway, restaurants, 5minutes walk from the Time Square. Luiz is a very friendly person as well. It was very nice to meet him and have stayed in his place.',15);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo87170',124,'2021-07-07',5,'I really recommend staying here! The Location is hard to beat and the room is clean and spaceous... Luiz was always reachable and made everything to ensure a nice stay! Anytime again!',28);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam39115',815,'2020-07-15',4,'The apartement was awesome. The room was very large and confortable and everything was very clean. Luiz was very kind. The only problem is that the toilet is outside the apartement, so you always need to go out. It is very well connected to the rest of the city with the bus or the subway. I strongly recommend it!',25);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('cursus11108',2472,'2021-09-12',4,'We ve stayed three nights at the Apartment, overall its a nice, clean, save and cosy place. The location, just 5mins from Times Square, is fabulouse! We didn t meet our host, but Regina was really nice! We would sleep der again.',1);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('ucc15',4818,'2017-01-15',5,'We had a wonderful time in New York City! This was the perfect location to explore the city as it was close to the Port Authority Bus/Subway station (2min walk) and close to the Time Square Subway (5min walk). The apartment was clean and the perfect amount of space for the two of us. The room s window did not face the street so it was rather quiet for New York standards as we could only hear the occasional siren. The location totally makes up for having to walk down the hall to the bathroom. Thanks Regina and Cleber.',4);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('platea7440',3204,'2021-06-29',3,'Great host. Met us earlier than check in time for our convenience. Very nice and friendly and easy to reach. Place was very clean and close to everything. Very enjoyable experience',25);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('lorem1829',2177,'2019-10-12',5,'It was really nice to stay at Cleber s place. The location of the apt is just perfect!',16);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('vestibulum0126',137,'2016-02-14',5,'The location of the apartment is perfect. It is close to the Times Square and very close to the Port Authority station. The room is very nice. Good lights, good bed, it was very clean. We had an issue with the key hole of the bathroom, but Cleber answered very promptly and helped to solve it. I recommend this apartment to anyone who wants to have access to the main points of NYC and have a confortable stay.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('commodo41119',185,'2016-03-22',4,'I stayed at Cleber s 3 nights and everything was perfect. Location is fantastic, apartment itself it super clean and cozy. And Cleber is nice as a person, professional with checking in and out. I would def recommend to stay here.',0);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('quam39115',385,'2019-05-18',5,'Great App, very clean, perfect located; Cleber is a real nice host, very patient and funny. Would book this room definetely again',15);
INSERT INTO accommodations_comments (user_id, accommodation_id, comment_date, rating, comment, comment_likes) VALUES ('dictumst76178',1121,'2020-05-10',5,'Everything was great. The location is very convenient, the place is clean. I liked staying there and would come back if I am in NYC again!',14);
